heading_context: Update or surrender your registered trade marks
chunks.html_content:
You must tell the Intellectual Property Office (IPO) if any of the details held in the trade mark register need updating or correcting.

You must also tell IPO if you want to give up your rights to your trade mark or appoint a representative or agent.
chunks.plain_content:
Update or surrender your registered trade marks 
You must tell the Intellectual Property Office (IPO) if any of the details held in the trade mark register need updating or correcting.
You must also tell IPO if you want to give up your rights to your trade mark or appoint a representative or agent.

heading_context: Update or surrender your registered trade marks
chunks.html_content: You don’t pay a fee to update the register.
chunks.plain_content:
Update or surrender your registered trade marks 
You don’t pay a fee to update the register.

heading_context: Update or surrender your registered trade marks
chunks.html_content:
Fill in a request to update a trade mark owner’s personal details to change your:

  • name
  • address
  • email
chunks.plain_content:
Update or surrender your registered trade marks 
Update your personal details
Fill in a request to update a trade mark owner’s personal details to change your:

  name
  address
  email

heading_context: Update or surrender your registered trade marks
Give up (‘surrender’) your rights to a trade mark
chunks.html_content:
Fill in either a:

  • notice to surrender a registered trade mark - to give up all your rights in a trade mark
  • notice to partially surrender a registration - if you only want to give up some of your rights
chunks.plain_content:
Update or surrender your registered trade marks 
Give up (‘surrender’) your rights to a trade mark
Fill in either a:

  
notice to surrender a registered trade mark - to give up all your rights in a trade mark
  
notice to partially surrender a registration - if you only want to give up some of your rights

heading_context: Update or surrender your registered trade marks
Correct a mistake on the register
chunks.html_content:
Fill in the application to rectify the register to correct:

  • a mistake you made, eg in your personal details
  • any mistakes in the wording

heading_context: Update or surrender your registered trade marks
Appoint or change an agent or representative
chunks.html_content: Fill in the form to appoint or change a representative to manage your registered trade marks. You can also use this form to update a current representative’s details, for example their address.
